    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到 Number Way！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Number Way</i> 是一款充满活力且引人入胜的益智冒险游戏，每一步都至关重要。你将在一个色彩斑斓的棋盘上移动，连接带数字的格子，体验通往终点格子的乐趣。操作简单、挑战巧妙，是休闲玩家和益智爱好者的理想选择。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法说明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个关卡中，你需要通过连接相邻的格子来绘制路径——只允许水平或垂直移动。你的目标是让路径上所有格子的数字之和，等于粉色格子的目标值。为了完成关卡，你的路径最后还必须停在粉色格子相邻的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/7a2bf0a99fc9bb743a4b5c6aa66deee1.poster.avif?t=1744397153\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/7a2bf0a99fc9bb743a4b5c6aa66deee1.webm?t=1744397153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/7a2bf0a99fc9bb743a4b5c6aa66deee1.mp4?t=1744397153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**直观的益智机制：**在充满活力的棋盘上连接格子，使其数字总和等于目标值。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**130 个独特关卡：**多样化的谜题，难度逐步升级，持续带来新挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**特殊格子：**发现具有额外效果的独特格子，帮助你破解最难的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**挑战 Boss 战：**在特殊关卡中对抗风格各异的 Boss，考验你的技巧与精准度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**轻松却富有挑战性：**简单易上手的操作，深度十足的玩法，令人欲罢不能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/9694f7ac01c4f75c6577f3cc8434136b.poster.avif?t=1744397153\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/9694f7ac01c4f75c6577f3cc8434136b.webm?t=1744397153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262770/extras/9694f7ac01c4f75c6577f3cc8434136b.mp4?t=1744397153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是精心计划每一步，还是想快速轻松地玩几局，<i>Number Way</i> 都能为你带来焕然一新的益智体验。锻炼你的策略，听从直觉，看看你是否有能力征服整张棋盘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在 Number Way 中画出通往胜利的路径——每一步都可能改变结局！</strong></p>",
